snippet.title: Obey Me! -One master to rule them all!-
snippet.description:
The long-awaited, newest title from the Shall we date? series has been released!
A love simulation game in which you can make handsome demons do your bidding. Become the master of the seven demon brothers and enjoy life in the Devildom!
Obey Me!

◆Download it now
-Android
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nttsolmare.game.android.obeyme
　*This link cannot be used through the Japanese store.

-iOS
https://apps.apple.com/app/id1477167654
　* This link cannot be used through the Japanese store.

----------

◆The “Obey Me!” official website
http://shallwedate.jp/obeyme/en/
